I probably won't ask
all the questions,

00:09:14.610 --> 00:09:16.890
I went into that
professorial mode

00:09:16.890 --> 00:09:21.940
where you just kind of
ask questions ad nauseum.

00:09:21.940 --> 00:09:24.300
So I'll try to ask maybe
just two or three questions.

00:09:24.300 --> 00:09:28.080
And then, just to get them
primed for your questions,

00:09:28.080 --> 00:09:30.420
and then we'll turn
it over to you.

00:09:30.420 --> 00:09:33.510
When it is your turn
to ask questions,

00:09:33.510 --> 00:09:36.000
there will be a mic
set up right here

00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:38.850
in the center of the hallway.

00:09:38.850 --> 00:09:42.900
And we ask that you identify
yourself, where you're from,

00:09:42.900 --> 00:09:46.680
and ask as brief a
question as you can.

00:09:46.680 --> 00:09:47.430
OK?

